{"tid":2255072,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［行動post］萬聖節，聲援泰國示威者","createTime":"2020-10-23T09:10:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T10:06:18.000Z","uid":211994,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e772a381c8ad61104501b5ab4146ac5da7b2c6ba","tid":2255072,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><strong><span class=\"gold\">注意：任何活動皆有風險，請自行決定<br />\n出去嘅人，小心啲<br />\n留喺屋企，準備隨時支援<br />\n<br />\n另外，活動搞手表明是此活動為</span><em><span class=\"red\">和理非</span></em><span class=\"gold\">性質。<br />\n詳細請睇下文<br />\n話雖如此，大家都要時刻打醒精神，執生。</span><br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NbQTnce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNbQTnce.jpg&h=ec41e604&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家好！我係上年Masquerade Halloween(哈囉喂狗官面具夜)嘅搞手之一。仲未知道今年Halloween有咩做？繼上年Halloween 後，今年Halloween 又有新搞作！<br />\n<br />\n活動名稱: 哈囉喂泰驚萬聖節<br />\n<br />\n活動時間: 10月31日(Halloween)夜晚7點開始<br />\n<br />\n活動地點: 各區(地點有待公布)<br />\n<br />\n活動定位: 主題為泰國，支持泰國手足，諷刺泰蝗。此活動並非大型聚人活動，並且係和理非活動。<br />\n<br />\n點解要搞依個活動？<br />\n<br />\n依家香港抗爭陷入樽頸，需要一啲創新活動。另外，今年Halloween啱啱好遇到泰國抗爭，泰國手足需要國際嘅關注同支持，此活動用一個唔同嘅方式表態同向泰國政府示威，諷刺泰蝗，而且增加港人對泰國示威嘅關注。最後，依家大規模聚人示威遊行聚到人嘅可能性低，且成本高，需要試下其他新形式同較低風險嘅活動，be water。<br />\n<br />\n活動流程:  我哋嘅義工會喺各區扮泰蝗(戴住泰蝗恐怖版面具，將來我哋會將面具嘅原檔攞上grp，大家都可以一齊扮)(大概地點將會日後公布)搵到泰蝗之後，影低佢擺上唔同嘅社交媒體(例如Twitter,IG)然後tag #milkteaalliance，#standwiththailand，#halloweenthaiscareyou，然後答啱佢問你關於泰國抗爭嘅問題，仲有糖同其他神秘嘢收！<br />\n<br />\n備註: 本活動沒有任何party成份。建議參加者戴唔同嘅面具同萬聖節裝扮加強氣氛，關於時政就更加好。<br />\n<br />\n上年我哋係唔同社交平台都被質疑為鬼，但努力同成果有目共睹。希望大家停止捉鬼，要捉鬼嘅嚟我哋活動捉飽佢。😤<br />\n<br />\n人心比鬼更可怕！<br />\n<br />\n如果有任何意見、查詢、問題，請加入公海討論。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/halloweenthaiscareyougrp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhalloweenthaiscareyougrp&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=0b38bac4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/halloweenthaiscareyougrp</a><br />\n<br />\n關於活動嘅最新消息請參考此channel:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/halloweenthaiscareyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhalloweenthaiscareyou&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vMF4Sk7tP0df8nBEIt5zy0g%3D&h=23d1e23b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/halloweenthaiscareyou</a><br />\n<br />\n更多詳細將會在此channel更新！<br />\n<br />\n另外希望大家將依個活動同channel link share去唔同地方(telegram group/Facebook/IG/連登等)因為你嘅每一個share都會令依個活動踏出一大步，多謝你哋！<br />\n<br />\n#standwithThailand<br />\n#三大訴求"},{"pid":"175ce948b6bb3e8781c625e80a76b4bd813ff5be","tid":2255072,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:14:48.000Z","msg":"撞"},{"pid":"dab9e275497039ba5d923342b6081fc10eb87ec6","tid":2255072,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:15:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"83e1e8dedb222bed7779142e7cb90eb8e2e9bee0","tid":2255072,"uid":324629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:16:54.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"412a94eb1029d26022f7c664d1b0f0466bdfb0ee","tid":2255072,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:23:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aca00a7a7dffbd27f1dbe3dfcb2bf3c3fc2bc25f","tid":2255072,"uid":296866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:36:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"42c6be3fd85c4f2629f1db5d24f581d836f3c8be","tid":2255072,"uid":47208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T09:41:49.000Z","msg":"騎劫曬所有萬聖節裝飾既人做支持者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同舊年十一一樣，個idea幾頂癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc1d776784342b2f56d6805edd13ccbfa617b63f","tid":2255072,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23